# {{mod_prefix}}_testing_eval_condition — condition wrapper for the testing hub.
#
# Compiled scenes route eligible condition-function calls through this wrapper
# so the testing hub can substitute a preview value at runtime without
# monkey-patching.  In normal gameplay the override dict is None and the
# wrapper short-circuits to the original function call.

